examples.en: Wrinkles deepen as we grow old.
Her face was a mass of wrinkles.
His brow is grooved out with wrinkles.
Ironing gets rid of most wrinkles.
He has added some new wrinkles to his game.
Her face was rough, and ploughed with wrinkles.
The trouble with linen is that it wrinkles so easily.
They finally have the wrinkles pretty well ironed out.
No one can avoid lines and wrinkles as they get older.
Laugh wrinkles rayed out from the corners of the old man's eyes.
The photo had been retouched to remove the wrinkles around his eyes.
The threat of skin cancer  not to mention the prospect of wrinkles  should be sufficient goad for using sunscreen.
